meanings: (하고 싶다) (동사로 쓰여) want (to), would like to, wish (to), (formal) desire (to), feel like (doing)
(~한 생각이 들다) (동사로 쓰여) look, seem, appear
레스토랑 찾기 I'd like to make a reservation.
호텔에서 I'd like to settle my account.
호텔에서 I'd like to settle up.

examples.korean: ‘I’d love to hear about it, but I’m late already.’ ‘That’s OK—it’ll keep. 발음듣기 “그 얘기도 듣고 싶은데 내가 이미 늦었어.” “괜찮아. 나중에 들어도 될 테니까.” Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
